</div>
<ul><li>January 27 =E2=80=93 <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ca=
spian_Airlines_Flight_6936" title=3D"Caspian Airlines Flight 6936">Caspian =
Airlines Flight 6936</a></b>, a McDonnell Douglas MD-83, flying a domestic =
flight from Tehran, Iran, overruns the runway on landing at Mahshahr Airpor=
t, Iran; the aircraft comes to a stop on a road, injuring 2 of the 144 pass=
engers and crew on board.</li>
<li>February 5 =E2=80=93 <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pegasu=
s_Airlines_Flight_2193" title=3D"Pegasus Airlines Flight 2193">Pegasus Airl=
ines Flight 2193</a></b>, a Boeing 737-800 operating a domestic flight betw=
een =C4=B0zmir and Istanbul in Turkey, skids off the runway and drops down =
an embankment on landing at Sabiha G=C3=B6k=C3=A7en International Airport; =
three of the 183 people on board are killed.</li>
<li>May 4 =E2=80=93 <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2020_East_A=
frican_Express_Airways_Brasilia_crash" title=3D"2020 East African Express A=
irways Brasilia crash">An East African Express Airways Embraer EMB 120 Bras=
ilia crashes</a></b> after being fired upon by Ethiopian ground forces duri=
ng a charter cargo flight carrying pandemic relief supplies to Berdale, Som=
alia; all four passengers and two crew are killed.</li>
<li>May 22 =E2=80=93 <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pakistan_I=
nternational_Airlines_Flight_8303" title=3D"Pakistan International Airlines=
 Flight 8303">Pakistan International Airlines Flight 8303</a></b>, an Airbu=
s A320, crashes in a residential neighborhood in Karachi minutes before a s=
econd attempted landing at Jinnah International Airport. 2 passengers survi=
ve among the 99 on board. One victim on the ground later dies from her inju=
ries.</li>
<li>August 7 =E2=80=93 <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Air_Indi=
a_Express_Flight_1344" title=3D"Air India Express Flight 1344">Air India Ex=
press Flight 1344</a></b>, a Boeing 737-800 operating an international repa=
triation flight, crashes on landing at Kozhikode International Airport, ski=
dding off the runway and plunging into a gorge; 21 occupants are killed, in=
cluding both pilots.</li>
<li>August 22 =E2=80=93 A <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2020_=
South_West_Aviation_Antonov_An-26_crash" title=3D"2020 South West Aviation =
Antonov An-26 crash">South West Aviation Antonov An-26 crashes</a></b> in a=
 residential area after taking off for a charter cargo flight from Juba Int=
ernational Airport, South Sudan, killing 8 of 9 people on board.</li>
<li>November 13 =E2=80=93 <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Volga=
-Dnepr_Airlines_Flight_4066" title=3D"Volga-Dnepr Airlines Flight 4066">Vol=
ga-Dnepr Airlines Flight 4066</a></b>, an An-124 operating a cargo flight f=
rom Novosibirsk, Russia to Vienna, Austria, suffers an uncontained engine f=
ailure on takeoff and overruns the runway upon returning to Novosibirsk. Al=
l 14 crew members survive the incident.</li></ul>
<h3><span class=3D"mw-headline" id=3D"2021">2021</span><span class=3D"mw-ed=
itsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https:=
//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DList_of_accidents_and_incidents_invo=
lving_commercial_aircraft&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D111" title=3D"Edi=
t section: 2021">edit</a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></s=
pan></h3>
<ul><li>January 9 =E2=80=93 <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sri=
wijaya_Air_Flight_182" title=3D"Sriwijaya Air Flight 182">Sriwijaya Air Fli=
ght 182</a></b>, a Boeing 737-500 operating a domestic flight to Pontianak,=
 Indonesia, crashes shortly after takeoff from Jakarta=E2=80=99s Soekarno=
=E2=80=93Hatta International Airport. All 62 passengers and crew are killed=
 in the crash.</li>
<li>February 20 =E2=80=93 <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Longt=
ail_Aviation_Flight_5504" title=3D"Longtail Aviation Flight 5504">Longtail =
Aviation Flight 5504</a> </b>, a Boeing 747-400BCF operating a cargo flight=
 from Maastricht, Netherlands to New York, United States suffers engine fai=
lure shortly after takeoff. The aircraft safely diverts to Liege, Belgium b=
ut two people on the ground are injured by falling debris.</li>
<li>February 20 =E2=80=93 <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unite=
d_Airlines_Flight_328" title=3D"United Airlines Flight 328">United Airlines=
 Flight 328</a></b>, a Boeing 777-200 flying from Denver to Honolulu suffer=
s an uncontained engine failure after <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w=
iki/Takeoff" title=3D"Takeoff">takeoff</a>, scattering debris over resident=
ial neighborhoods below. The plane uses the remaining engine to safely land=
 in Denver, none of the 241 passengers and crew are injured, nor was anyone=
 injured on the ground from debris.</li>
<li>March 2 =E2=80=93 A <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2021_So=
uth_Sudan_Supreme_Airlines_Let_L-410_Turbolet_crash" class=3D"mw-redirect" =
title=3D"2021 South Sudan Supreme Airlines Let L-410 Turbolet crash">South =
Sudan Supreme Airlines Let L-410 Turbolet crashes</a></b> whilst operating =
a domestic flight from Pieri to Yuai, South Sudan. All 8 passengers and 2 c=
rew are killed.</li>
<li>May 12 =E2=80=93 <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2021_Cente=
nnial_Airport_mid-air_collision" title=3D"2021 Centennial Airport mid-air c=
ollision">Key Lime Air Flight 970</a></b>, a Swearingen Metroliner on a cha=
rtered cargo flight from Salida, Colorado, collides with a Cirrus SR22 on a=
pproach to Centennial Airport, Colorado. The Cirrus crash-lands in a nearby=
 field whilst the Swearingen Metroliner makes an emergency landing. All thr=
ee occupants on both aircraft survive.</li>
<li>May 23  =E2=80=93 <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ryanair_F=
light_4978" title=3D"Ryanair Flight 4978">Ryanair Flight 4978</a></b>, a Bo=
eing 737-800 operating an international scheduled passenger flight from Ath=
ens, Greece to Vilnius, Lithuania, is forced to land at Minsk, Belarus, esc=
orted by a Belarusian Air Force MiG-29. Activist Roman Pratasevich, who was=
 on board the aircraft, is arrested.</li></ul>
<div class=3D"thumb tright"><div class=3D"thumbinner" style=3D"width:222px;=
"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Forward_Fuselage_Transair_8=
10.png" class=3D"image"><img alt=3D"" src=3D"https://upload.wikimedia.org/w=
ikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9d/Forward_Fuselage_Transair_810.png/220px-Forward=
_Fuselage_Transair_810.png" decoding=3D"async" width=3D"220" height=3D"147"=
 class=3D"thumbimage" data-file-width=3D"720" data-file-height=3D"480"></a>=
  <div class=3D"thumbcaption"><div class=3D"magnify"><a href=3D"https://en.=
wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Forward_Fuselage_Transair_810.png" class=3D"interna=
l" title=3D"Enlarge"></a></div>Transair Flight 810</div></div></div>
<ul><li>July 2 =E2=80=93 <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Transa=
ir_Flight_810" title=3D"Transair Flight 810">Transair Flight 810</a></b>, a=
 Boeing 737-200C operating a domestic cargo flight in Hawaii between Honolu=
lu, Oahu and the neighbouring island of Maui, suffers engine failure shortl=
y after takeoff and ditches in the sea. Both pilots survive with injuries.<=
/li>
<li>July 6 =E2=80=93 <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Petropavlo=
vsk-Kamchatsky_Air_Flight_251_(2021)" title=3D"Petropavlovsk-Kamchatsky Air=
 Flight 251 (2021)">Petropavlovsk-Kamchatsky Air Enterprise Flight 251</a><=
/b>, an Antonov An-26 operating a domestic flight from Petropavlovsk-Kamcha=
tsky to Palana, Russia, crashes on approach. All 22 passengers and 6 crew a=
re killed</li>
<li>July 16 =E2=80=93 <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Siberian_=
Light_Aviation_Flight_42" title=3D"Siberian Light Aviation Flight 42">Siber=
ian Light Aviation Flight 42</a></b>, an Antonov An-28 operating a domestic=
 flight from Kedrovy to Tomsk, Russia, makes a crash landing after takeoff,=
 injuring 11 of the 18 passengers and crew on board.</li>
<li>September 12 =E2=80=93 <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sibe=
rian_Light_Aviation_Flight_51" title=3D"Siberian Light Aviation Flight 51">=
Siberian Light Aviation Flight 51</a></b>, a Let L-410 operating a domestic=
 flight from Irkutsk to Kazachinskoye, Russia, crashes in a forest short of=
 the runway while attempting to land in heavy fog. 4 of the 16 occupants ar=
e killed and the 12 survivors are seriously injured.</li></ul>
<div class=3D"thumb tright"><div class=3D"thumbinner" style=3D"width:222px;=
"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:N987AK_wreckage_-_1.jpg" cl=
ass=3D"image"><img alt=3D"" src=3D"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/c=
ommons/thumb/f/f7/N987AK_wreckage_-_1.jpg/220px-N987AK_wreckage_-_1.jpg" de=
coding=3D"async" width=3D"220" height=3D"140" class=3D"thumbimage" data-fil=
e-width=3D"1000" data-file-height=3D"638"></a>  <div class=3D"thumbcaption"=
><div class=3D"magnify"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:N987A=
K_wreckage_-_1.jpg" class=3D"internal" title=3D"Enlarge"></a></div>987 Inve=
stments LLC <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/McDonnell_Douglas_MD-8=
7" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"McDonnell Douglas MD-87">McDonnell Dougla=
s MD-87</a> N987AK</div></div></div>
<ul><li>October 19 =E2=80=93 In the <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/=
wiki/2021_Houston_MD-87_crash" title=3D"2021 Houston MD-87 crash">2021 Hous=
ton MD-87 crash</a></b>, a McDonnell Douglas MD-87 aircraft crashes on take=
-off from Houston Executive Airport, Houston, Texas. All 21 people on board=
 survive.</li>
<li>November 3 =E2=80=93 <b><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grodno=
_Aviakompania_Flight_1252" title=3D"Grodno Aviakompania Flight 1252">Grodno=
 Aviakompania Flight 1252</a></b>, an An-12, crashes whilst attempting to l=
and at Irkutsk International Airport, Russia whilst operating a cargo fligh=
t. All 9 aboard are killed.</li></ul>
